ÉThe Royal Parks are not a luxury, they are a uecessity
Can you imagine London without them?

Eight amazing parks where history and nature share roots
helping us to feel happier and healthier

Bringing the magic of the Royal Parks to life.
May 2003 - July 2017

This bench celebrates the wonderful work of the
Royal Parks Foundation

Thank you to the inspirational team of
Trustees, Employees and Volunteers who love these parks

500 years of history and 5,000 acres of precious green-space
in the heart of London"ö
